♪ I'm gonna ride ♪

00:18.268 --> 00:20.228
♪ I'm riding free ♪

00:20.311 --> 00:22.272
♪ So come along, let's go along ♪

00:22.355 --> 00:24.399
♪ Come on the journey with me ♪

00:24.482 --> 00:26.317
♪ I'm gonna ride ♪

00:26.401 --> 00:28.403
♪ I'm riding free ♪

00:28.486 --> 00:30.530
♪ As long as I am here with you ♪

00:30.613 --> 00:32.741
♪ I feel the spirit within me ♪

00:32.824 --> 00:34.868
-♪ Yeah, eh, eh ♪
